text: Charles XV & IV also Carl (Carl Ludvig Eugen); Swedish and Norwegian: Karl, born 3 May 1826, dead 18 September 1872, was a Swedish monarch. He was the King of Sweden (Charles XV) and Norway (Charles IV) from 1859 until his death in 1872. == References == ==Other websites== Category:1826 births Category:1872 deaths Category:Kings and Queens of Sweden Category:People from Stockholm
title: Charles XV
